{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ac04aa03b3","title":"致周恩来等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23b1727988","index":0,"year":1940,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"ac04aa03b3"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"310b7ebb0a","type":"paragraph","text":"致周恩来等电“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"ac04aa03b3"},{"id":"5aeea49195","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年11月12日）你们应得转介石调动二十九个师进攻新四军的事实公开宣布不应秘密。你们应向各方宣传上述军队准备大规模进攻的严重形，如果打响，就是大规模内战，酪蚌相争，只使日本人渔人得利。目前苏北业已和平，如又发生战争，新四军不能不自卫，八路车亦不能坐视，鲜由彼启，我们不能负责。你们应向各方奔走时，为制止内战换教危亡而奋斗这是毛泽东致周思来、李克农、项英、陈数、刘少奇、黄克诚、彭","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"ac04aa03b3"}],"page":{"id":"4006585883","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"ac04aa03b3","start":219,"end":219}}}},"__N_SSG":true}